task.summary: Added IDE setup files, updated gitignore to ignore the CMake output files that are automatically produced by CLion.
Changed to read and support temperature in data sentences. Now switches to white circle as airball when the IAS is too small to reasonably display.
Improve probe math to match what was written in 2016 paper.
The main deployment binary, ab_device, was erroneously configured to use fake data. Fixed.
Adds gradually fading TAS ring to the display.
